<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Reset Password</title>
  <style>
    /* Custom CSS styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3ccff;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f5f5f7;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #333;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #5e336f;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .url {
      display: block;
      color: #fff;
      margin-top: 10px;
      word-break: break-all;
      background: #E5D4FF;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Reset Password</h1>
    <p>Hey <%= userName %>,</p>
    <p>We're here, no need to fear...</p>
    <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
    <p><a href="<%= url %>">Reset Your Password</a></p>
    <p>If you're having trouble clicking the reset password button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:
    </p>
    <p class="url">
      <%= url %>
    </p>
    <p>If you did not request this email, you can safely ignore it.</p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>